# Goals

## Cli-G1 CLI Mode provides interactive REPL chat as forge chat subcommand
**Status:** draft
**Tags:** stack:backend
**Depends on:** Provider-G1

CLI mode was ported from auto-code-rs but removed because AutoForge is a Web UI-driven system — a CLI REPL is not part of its core workflow. The provider, runtime, and tool modules remain; only the CLI entry point and REPL loop were removed.
